The paper deals with a model of price competition and welfare analysis, which falls under the domain of game theory and mechanism design. Therefore, cs.GT (Game Theory and Mechanism Design) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also discusses the online sale of consumer goods, which is related to e-commerce, and airline pricing, which is related to transportation. Therefore, cs.EC (E-commerce and Online Markets) and cs.IT (Information Theory) are also likely sub-categories. The paper uses mathematical analysis to study the model, which suggests that it may also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
